{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'd like to apologize, first of all, to all of you"},{"time":3000,"text":"because I have no form"},{"time":5000,"text":"of PowerPoint presentation."},{"time":8000,"text":"So what I'm going to do"},{"time":10000,"text":"is, every now and again, I will make this gesture,"},{"time":12000,"text":"and in a moment of PowerPoint democracy,"},{"time":14000,"text":"you can imagine what you'd like to see."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18000,"text":"I do a radio show."},{"time":20000,"text":"The radio show is called \"The Infinite Monkey Cage.\""},{"time":23000,"text":"It's about science, it's about rationalism."},{"time":26000,"text":"So therefore, we get a lot of complaints"},{"time":28000,"text":"every single week --"},{"time":30000,"text":"complaints including one we get very often,"},{"time":33000,"text":"which is to say the very title, \"Infinite Monkey Cage,\""},{"time":36000,"text":"celebrates the idea of vivisection."},{"time":39000,"text":"We have made it quite clear to these people"},{"time":41000,"text":"that an infinite monkey cage is roomy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":46000,"text":"We also had someone else who said,"},{"time":48000,"text":"\"'The Infinite Monkey Cage' idea is ridiculous."},{"time":50000,"text":"An infinite number of monkeys"},{"time":52000,"text":"could never write the works of Shakespeare."},{"time":54000,"text":"We know this because they did an experiment.\""},{"time":57000,"text":"Yes, they gave 12 monkeys a typewriter for a week,"},{"time":61000,"text":"and after a week, they only used it as a bathroom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":64000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":66000,"text":"So the main element though, the main complaint we get --"},{"time":68000,"text":"and one that I find most worrying --"},{"time":70000,"text":"is that people say, \"Oh, why do you insist"},{"time":73000,"text":"on ruining the magic?"},{"time":75000,"text":"You bring in science, and it ruins the magic.\""},{"time":77000,"text":"Now I'm an arts graduate;"},{"time":79000,"text":"I love myth and magic"},{"time":81000,"text":"and existentialism and self-loathing."},{"time":83000,"text":"That's what I do."},{"time":85000,"text":"But I also don't understand"},{"time":87000,"text":"how it does ruin the magic."},{"time":89000,"text":"All of the magic, I think,"},{"time":91000,"text":"that may well be taken away by science"},{"time":93000,"text":"is then replaced by something as wonderful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95000,"text":"Astrology, for instance:"},{"time":97000,"text":"like many rationalists, I'm a Pisces."},{"time":100000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":103000,"text":"Now astrology --"},{"time":105000,"text":"we remove the banal idea"},{"time":107000,"text":"that your life could be predicted;"},{"time":109000,"text":"that you'll, perhaps today, meet a lucky man"},{"time":111000,"text":"who's wearing a hat."},{"time":113000,"text":"That is gone."},{"time":115000,"text":"But if we want to look at the sky and see predictions, we still can."},{"time":118000,"text":"We can see predictions of galaxies forming,"},{"time":121000,"text":"of galaxies colliding into each other, of new solar systems."},{"time":124000,"text":"This is a wonderful thing."},{"time":126000,"text":"If the Sun could one day -- and indeed the Earth, in fact --"},{"time":129000,"text":"if the Earth could read its own astrological, astronomical chart,"},{"time":133000,"text":"one day it would say,"},{"time":135000,"text":"\"Not a good day for making plans."},{"time":137000,"text":"You'll been engulfed by a red giant.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":139000,"text":"And that to me as well,"},{"time":141000,"text":"that if you think I'm worried about losing worlds,"},{"time":144000,"text":"well Many Worlds theory --"},{"time":146000,"text":"one of the most beautiful, fascinating,"},{"time":149000,"text":"sometimes terrifying ideas"},{"time":151000,"text":"from the quantum interpretation --"},{"time":153000,"text":"is a wonderful thing."},{"time":155000,"text":"That every person here, every decision that you've made today,"},{"time":158000,"text":"every decision you've made in your life,"},{"time":160000,"text":"you've not really made that decision,"},{"time":162000,"text":"but in fact, every single permutation of those decisions"},{"time":166000,"text":"is made, each one going off into a new universe."},{"time":169000,"text":"That is a wonderful idea."},{"time":171000,"text":"If you ever think that your life is rubbish,"},{"time":175000,"text":"always remember"},{"time":177000,"text":"there's another you that's made much worse decisions than that."},{"time":180000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":182000,"text":"If you ever think, \"Ah, I want to end it all,\""},{"time":184000,"text":"don't end it all."},{"time":186000,"text":"Remember that in the majority of universes,"},{"time":188000,"text":"you don't even exist in the first place."},{"time":190000,"text":"This to me, in its own strange way,"},{"time":193000,"text":"is very, very comforting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195000,"text":"Now reincarnation, that's another thing gone -- the afterlife."},{"time":197000,"text":"But it's not gone."},{"time":199000,"text":"Science actually says"},{"time":201000,"text":"we will live forever."},{"time":204000,"text":"Well, there is one proviso."},{"time":206000,"text":"We won't actually live forever. You won't live forever."},{"time":209000,"text":"Your consciousness, the you-ness of you, the me-ness of me --"},{"time":212000,"text":"that gets this one go."},{"time":215000,"text":"But every single thing that makes us,"},{"time":217000,"text":"every atom in us,"},{"time":219000,"text":"has already created a myriad of different things"},{"time":222000,"text":"and will go on to create a myriad of new things."},{"time":225000,"text":"We have been mountains"},{"time":228000,"text":"and apples and pulsars"},{"time":230000,"text":"and other people's knees."},{"time":232000,"text":"Who knows, maybe one of your atoms was once Napoleon's knee."},{"time":235000,"text":"That is a good thing."},{"time":237000,"text":"Unlike the occupants of the universe,"},{"time":239000,"text":"the universe itself is not wasteful."},{"time":242000,"text":"We are all totally recyclable."},{"time":244000,"text":"And when we die,"},{"time":246000,"text":"we don't even have to be placed in different refuse sacs."},{"time":249000,"text":"This is a wonderful thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251000,"text":"Understanding, to me,"},{"time":253000,"text":"does not remove the wonder and the joy."},{"time":257000,"text":"For instance, my wife could turn to me and she may say,"},{"time":260000,"text":"\"Why do you love me?\""},{"time":262000,"text":"And I can with all honesty"},{"time":264000,"text":"look her in the eye and say,"},{"time":266000,"text":"\"Because our pheromones"},{"time":268000,"text":"matched our olfactory receptors.\""},{"time":271000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":273000,"text":"Though I'll probably also say something"},{"time":275000,"text":"about her hair and personality as well."},{"time":277000,"text":"And that is a wonderful thing there."},{"time":280000,"text":"Love does not die because of that thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282000,"text":"Pain doesn't go away either."},{"time":284000,"text":"This is a terrible thing, even though I understand pain."},{"time":286000,"text":"If someone punches me --"},{"time":288000,"text":"and because of my personality,"},{"time":290000,"text":"this is recently a regular occurrence --"},{"time":292000,"text":"I understand where the pain comes from."},{"time":294000,"text":"It is basically momentum to energy"},{"time":297000,"text":"where the four-vector is constant -- that's what it is."},{"time":299000,"text":"But at no point can I react and go,"},{"time":301000,"text":"\"Ha! Is that the best momentum-to-energy fourth vector constant you've got?\""},{"time":306000,"text":"No, I just spit out a tooth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":310000,"text":"And that is all of these different things -- the love for my child."},{"time":313000,"text":"I have a son. His name is Archie."},{"time":315000,"text":"I'm very lucky,"},{"time":317000,"text":"because he's better than all the other children."},{"time":319000,"text":"Now I know you don't think that."},{"time":321000,"text":"You may well have your own children"},{"time":323000,"text":"and think, \"Oh no, my child's best.\""},{"time":326000,"text":"That's the wonderful thing about evolution --"},{"time":328000,"text":"the predilection to believe"},{"time":330000,"text":"that our child is best."},{"time":332000,"text":"Now in many ways, that's just a survival thing."},{"time":335000,"text":"The fact we see here is the vehicle for our genes,"},{"time":338000,"text":"and therefore we love it."},{"time":340000,"text":"But we don't notice that bit; we just unconditionally love."},{"time":343000,"text":"That is a wonderful thing."},{"time":345000,"text":"Though I should say that my son is best"},{"time":347000,"text":"and is better than your children."},{"time":350000,"text":"I've done some tests."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352000,"text":"And all of these things to me"},{"time":354000,"text":"give such joy and excitement and wonder."},{"time":357000,"text":"Even quantum mechanics can give you an excuse"},{"time":360000,"text":"for bad housework, for instance."},{"time":362000,"text":"Perhaps you've been at home for a week on your own."},{"time":365000,"text":"You house is in a terrible state."},{"time":367000,"text":"Your partner is about to return."},{"time":369000,"text":"You think, what should I do?"},{"time":371000,"text":"Do nothing."},{"time":373000,"text":"All you have to do"},{"time":375000,"text":"is, when she walks in, using a quantum interpretation,"},{"time":377000,"text":"say, \"I'm so sorry."},{"time":379000,"text":"I stopped observing the house for a moment,"},{"time":381000,"text":"and when I started observing again,"},{"time":383000,"text":"everything had happened.\""},{"time":385000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":387000,"text":"That's the strong anthropic principle of vacuuming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":391000,"text":"For me, it's a very, very important thing."},{"time":393000,"text":"Even on my journey up here --"},{"time":395000,"text":"the joy that I have on my journey up here every single time."},{"time":397000,"text":"If you actually think, you remove the myth and there is still something wonderful."},{"time":400000,"text":"I'm sitting on a train."},{"time":402000,"text":"Every time I breathe in,"},{"time":404000,"text":"I'm breathing in a million-billion-billion"},{"time":406000,"text":"atoms of oxygen."},{"time":408000,"text":"I'm sitting on a chair."},{"time":410000,"text":"Even though I know the chair is made of atoms"},{"time":412000,"text":"and therefore actually in many ways empty space,"},{"time":414000,"text":"I find it comfortable."},{"time":416000,"text":"I look out the window, and I realize"},{"time":418000,"text":"that every single time we stop and I look out that window,"},{"time":420000,"text":"framed in that window,"},{"time":422000,"text":"wherever we are,"},{"time":424000,"text":"I am observing more life"},{"time":426000,"text":"than there is in the rest of the known universe"},{"time":429000,"text":"beyond the planet Earth."},{"time":431000,"text":"If you go to the safari parks"},{"time":433000,"text":"on Saturn or Jupiter,"},{"time":435000,"text":"you will be disappointed."},{"time":437000,"text":"And I realize I'm observing this"},{"time":439000,"text":"with the brain, the human brain,"},{"time":441000,"text":"the most complex thing in the known universe."},{"time":444000,"text":"That, to me, is an incredible thing."},{"time":446000,"text":"And do you know what, that might be enough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":449000,"text":"Steven Weinberg, the Nobel laureate, once said,"},{"time":452000,"text":"\"The more the universe seems comprehensible,"},{"time":454000,"text":"the more it seems pointless.\""},{"time":456000,"text":"Now for some people,"},{"time":458000,"text":"that seems to lead to an idea of nihilism."},{"time":460000,"text":"But for me, it doesn't. That is a wonderful thing."},{"time":463000,"text":"I'm glad the universe is pointless."},{"time":465000,"text":"It means if I get to the end of my life,"},{"time":467000,"text":"the universe can't turn to me and go, \"What have you been doing, you idiot?"},{"time":470000,"text":"That's not the point.\""},{"time":472000,"text":"I can make my own purpose."},{"time":474000,"text":"You can make your own purpose."},{"time":476000,"text":"We have the individual power"},{"time":478000,"text":"to go, \"This is what I want to do.\""},{"time":480000,"text":"And in a pointless universe, that, to me, is a wonderful thing."},{"time":483000,"text":"I have chosen to make silly jokes"},{"time":485000,"text":"about quantum mechanics and the Copenhagen interpretation."},{"time":488000,"text":"You, I imagine, can do much better things with your time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491000,"text":"Thank you very much. Goodbye."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}